":"武漢肺炎肆虐令全城熱搶口罩，長和 （00001） 旗下百佳及屈臣氏網站都不勝負荷。百佳網站頁面顯示，網站正進行定期維修，短時間會恢復正常。屈臣氏網站雖正常運作，但若要進入屈臣氏網站，則要排隊等候近一小時。"},{"pid":"945cbfbf5cddf93d758c1a112f5482f67e129d21","tid":1849343,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:25:07.000Z","msg":"屈臣氏網上訂果批貨都未到手"},{"pid":"d6b1ba51a76a5ae37b199c7e64841b0eca6fd2a8","tid":1849343,"uid":51313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:25:31.000Z","msg":"同藍屍廢老一齊和你shop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad2dc6ec77fc080e63673357abf79cdb54337f9","tid":1849343,"uid":160662,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6a1e6328f0640bd2eb351fcbeeeeb29305c081bc","tid":1849343,"uid":212626,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8X2cqv1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8X2cqv1.png&h=01545de0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:25:50.000Z","msg":"唔駛排架嘞, 網上店無晒消毒野, 口罩"},{"pid":"b535c382b451eade740f6aa79e20efeb89d59495","tid":1849343,"uid":257622,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:26:19.000Z","msg":"其實買唔口罩都唔需要搶，口罩唔一定防到肺炎，只不過係心理好過一點"},{"pid":"5ed457b2f5fffae6ad30ef6b86a29765aaec82ba","tid":1849343,"uid":160662,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b535c382b451eade740f6aa79e20efeb89d59495","tid":1849343,"uid":257622,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:26:19.000Z","msg":"其實買唔口罩都唔需要搶，口罩唔一定防到肺炎，只不過係心理好過一點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:27:07.000Z","msg":"岩, 唔戴口罩, 由你做起"},{"pid":"cd685f0d3a40ab60ef7d03d4514aedfbd40db525","tid":1849343,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:27:43.000Z","msg":"「武漢肺炎」新型冠狀病毒近日在本港肆虐，有感疫情爆發市面上的口罩被搶購一空，一間入口泰國貨品的雜貨店，早前透過社交媒體公布將會特意入口一批3M防護口罩及一般外科口罩，並於今午(29日)發貨至各門市開始售賣。<br />\n<br />\n就東網記者現場所見，該雜貨店多間分店在今晨已大排長龍，<span style=\"color: red;\">其中在大埔超級城，該分店外便逾千人「打蛇餅」輪候</span>，而現場排隊人士亦大多戴上口罩。<br />\n<br />\n另外，<span style=\"color: red;\">在旺角區內多間藥房外，今晨亦出現大大小小多條人龍等候開門，惟至近10時商店陸續營業，多間藥房的口罩及消毒液早已售罄</span>，部分商店僅安排排隊人士限購消毒濕紙巾，有排隊人士失望而回。<br />\n<br />\n其中，任職資訊科技的陳先生指，今晨行經旺角時見到有人排隊，以為有口罩售賣，於是便加入排隊，豈料到藥房開門時始知無貨，惟有買數包濕紙巾了事。他亦透露，自己早前已在網上訂購一批口罩自用，但仍擔心不夠用。<br />\n<br />\n據指，慈雲山一間藥房外有排隊長者不適需坐下，現場亦有人鼓譟。"},{"pid":"a611e69529bb187610223f86ef5afa994336dc88","tid":1849343,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fad2dc6ec77fc080e63673357abf79cdb54337f9","tid":1849343,"uid":160662,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6a1e6328f0640bd2eb351fcbeeeeb29305c081bc","tid":1849343,"uid":212626,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8X2cqv1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8X2cqv1.png&h=01545de0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:25:50.000Z","msg":"唔駛排架嘞, 網上店無晒消毒野, 口罩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:28:31.000Z","msg":"見到個數字即刻閂咗個網<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23bd9aee2c0b92c2c9b5f8aab85ba8c0a1de2236","tid":1849343,"uid":212702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:28:39.000Z","msg":"好快全港暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce29d3e186a2042bb683e0d4507efe9cd43b12db","tid":1849343,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435a9900b001aa15642642229b420d9fd10902eb","tid":1849343,"uid":42536,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"26896027fb57b59af9937e13aae2e58b58026c9b","tid":1849343,"uid":196227,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"quote":{"pid":"4e43fed1f8df76a59fa435cd31a6aa78a965302a","tid":1